# Local-only OIDC interop fixtures — do NOT commit.
# A real OIDC token embeds the minting repo's identity (name, visibility) in its
# claims; publishing it from this public repo would disclose that repo
# (disclosure barrier, CLAUDE.md §0). Keep these local to run the GitHub OIDC
# interop test; CI runs the mock-based discovery/JWKS tests instead.
github_oidc_token.txt
github_oidc_jwks.json
